00:02:21.319 --> 00:02:26.349
In the beginning, it was characterized by
a new style of combat made possible by the

00:02:26.349 --> 00:02:31.689
mechanized technology of tanks, airplanes,
and especially, trucks. This was the Blitzkrieg,

00:02:31.689 --> 00:02:37.760
a devastating tactic combining quick movement
of troops, tanks, and massive use of air power

00:02:37.760 --> 00:02:42.269
to support infantry movements. And in the
